      "data": {
        "title": "Onboard The Model",
        "body": "Use the handshake button on the right side of the address bar to copy the onboarding contract to your clipboard. Paste it into the chat field in your chatbot and press enter. That contract teaches the LLM what declaration, markdown, port, and portal mean before you ask it for mutations.",
        "tag": "Concept",
