      "data": {
        "identity": {
          "graphId": "tutorial-bootstrap-llm"
        },
        "markdown": "## Example first graph request\n\nAfter the handshake, ask for a very small declaration-first graph. For example:\n\n```text\nCreate a small Twilite graph about why dragons would make terrible apartment pets.\n\nor\n\ncreate a graph about Goldilocks and the Three Bears\n\n```\n\nTry asking for changes.  \nIf you find yourself unable to do something you want to do, contact the developer (dev@twilite.zone).  This project is in active development.\n",
        "_placement": {
          "version": 1,
          "state": "manually-shaped",
          "source": "manual",
          "updatedAt": 1783087305719,
          "reason": "node-drag"
        }
      }
    },
