        "body": "1. Open your LLM in a fresh chat.\n2. Give it the Twilite onboarding contract.\n3. Ask for the JSON-only handshake.\n4. Ask for a tiny declaration-first graph in the current session.\n5. Confirm the result includes declaration, markdown, and an exposed reader port.\n6. Apply the result and confirm the graph loads.",
